      "title": "PROMPT",
      "properties": {
        "widget_ue_connectable": {}
      },
      "widgets_values": [
        "PROMPT 1 CAMERA CHASE\nCinematic NYC alley chase: The camera starts shoulder-height behind a hooded man steadily tracking forward as he weaves through crowds.\n\nPROMPT 2 CAMERA PAN\nA low angle shot of a of young man in dappled sunlight. Backlighting, warm low-saturation tones. Camera pans left to low angle shot of a cute girl\n\nPROMPT 3 CAMERA DOLL in/out\nIron Man sits in a sleek, futuristic metal chair inside a dimly lit industrial setting. He is fully suited in his iconic red and gold armor, the arc reactor glowing in his chest. Camera dollies out. \n\n\nPROMPT 4\na woman riding a hourse on grass field\n\nPROMPT 5\nA heroic fox knight in shining armor galloping across a misty medieval battlefield at dawn, camera slowly dollies in from wide establishing shot to closeup as sunlight breaks through fog; cinematic lighting, soft warm tones, epic atmosphere.\n\nPROMPT 6\nTwo anthropomorphic cats in comfy boxing gear and bright gloves fight intensely on a spotlighted stage with cheering crowd in the background, camera pans side-to-side to follow their punches, dynamic smoke and light beams slicing across.\n\nPROMPT 7\nA futuristic samurai gliding through a neon-lit cyberpunk city at night, sword drawn, reflections on rain‑wet streets, slow track shot under glowing signs, deep contrast and vibrant color grading.\n\nPROMPT 8\nA golden ladybug crawling across a bright yellow dandelion petal in soft sunlight, close macro focus, petals gently sway in breeze, shallow depth‑of‑field, warm cinematic feel.\n\nPROMPT 9\nA bustling kitchen in stylized animation: a chef flipping pancakes, steam rising, a cat weaving between countertops, utensils clattering; camera follows the cat then pans to chef’s reaction; bright, cheerful, warm tones.\n"
      ],
      "color": "#223",
      "bgcolor": "#335"
    },
